      :fill="changeColor"
    />

<script>
export default {
  name: "SvgIconDelete",
  props: {
    status: { type: Boolean, default: false },
  },
  data() {
    return {};
  },
  computed: {
    changeColor() {
      console.log("Status", this.status);
      if (!this.status) {
        return "#444444";
      } else {
        return "#A0A0A0";
      }
    },
  },
};
</script>
